Walkthrough

- Speak with Pherimociel at (G-6) in Ru'Lude Gardens for a cutscene.
- Head to the Marble Bridge (F-7) in Upper Jeuno and check the door for
  another cutscene.
  - Optional: Talk to Mojuro-Nojuro right outside.
