Category:Bastok Missions]] },
  { title = "Bastok Mission 5-1", walkthrough = [[Magicite |Next=Bastok Mission 5-2{{!}}Xarcabard, Land of Truths
|Title=Archlich Assassin |Reward= *Rank Points
